{"tid":1535553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[甩牙] 即刻拎埋隻牙去瑪麗, 有機會植返","createTime":"2019-09-03T11:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T13:04:05.000Z","uid":79410,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"36a433031acd945a278e38427cd70b41396b7a78","tid":1535553,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"好多人唔知甩咗牙. 係可以植返落去. <br />\n<br />\n市民如即時將恒齒放回原位，或存放入特定液體例如牛奶或生理鹽水，再往牙科診所求醫，日後有較大機會成功植回牙齒。<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140111/00410_010.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140111%2F00410_010.html&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=763d3b9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140111/00410_010.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我20年前住瑪麗, 隔離個小朋友踢波甩咗4隻牙. 菲臘牙科醫院教授幫佢植返. (唔係100%)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好唔理隻牙呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"f9531c76e34241d8b1971d79f17330d52c7bb556","tid":1535553,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:41:18.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？我們需要更多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530124</a>"},{"pid":"21252debd3d92a651ad23a997653582f532b73d8","tid":1535553,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:42:12.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"31ea742c261ffabfe35d8cd15c9ef7edb3c2b191","tid":1535553,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:45:10.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n5. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n6. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n7. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n8. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n9. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"b35919732fc7e79809e208b719309c4aafaf0201","tid":1535553,"uid":198866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:46:38.000Z","msg":"踢波磨甩左粒lin有冇得植返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbb3fcfac5573e3abb27f9c4aead0a25dac3253","tid":1535553,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6230784bcc4be2aae27e066da8905a0c13235023","tid":1535553,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b35919732fc7e79809e208b719309c4aafaf0201","tid":1535553,"uid":198866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:46:38.000Z","msg":"踢波磨甩左粒lin有冇得植返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"有. 塞返粒波子落去."},{"pid":"faad23cdb8f12427fc7bae10419336604c7be4e7","tid":1535553,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79de4a7712dc9b2a790addd21d5d33e0315ee173","tid":1535553,"uid":7